title: Large Renovated 1 Bedroom/1 Bathroom Apartment - Dog Friendly
posting_body: ['4141 4th Ave S, Unit 4, Minneapolis, MN 55409', 'September 1st', 'Availability.', 'Charming Fourplex.', 'Owner lives in one of the units.', 'Minutes from Downtown and Uptown!', 'Nice, open (780 sq ft) 1 bedroom/1 bathroom TOP floor apartment in the Bryant Neighborhood.', 'Apartment was renovated last year, new kitchen and bathroom!', 'Dogs are welcome, but subject to approval.', 'NO BREED RESTRICTIONS, 25 pound weight limit.', 'Unit has an open concept feel.', 'Room in the kitchen for a dining table.', 'Easy access to 35W and near 4 bus lines.', 'Several Minneapolis parks, lakes, and recreation areas are just a short distance away.', 'Seward Co-op within walking distance.', 'Come take a look at your new home Today!', 'Amenities', '-\tRenovated Kitchen and Bathroom', '-\tStainless Steel Appliances', '-\tEnclosed outside dog area', '-\tCoin operated laundry on site', '-\tOne storage unit included', '-\tOne Window AC provided and installed', '-\tElectronic locks', '-\tDishwasher', '-\tHardwood floors throughout', '-\tPantry', '-\tOff street parking available', '-\tOutside Grill', '-\tOutside Firepit', 'Availability and Lease Term', '-\tAvailable for rent September 1st, 2021', '-\tLease Term: 12 months', 'Utilities', '-\tTenant pays for electric and gas (for cooking and water heater only)', '-\tOwner pays heating gas, sewer, trash, and water', 'Occupancy Policy', '-\t1 Bedroom: 2 occupants maximum', 'DOGS WELCOME', '-\tDogs are welcome, but subject to approval.', 'NO BREED RESTRICTIONS, 25 pound weight limit', '-\tNo cats please', 'Application Fee & Dog Fees', '-\t', 'The application fee is $29.00 (plus tax) per applicant through <URL>', '-\tNon-refundable dog fee is $350.00 per dog.', 'NO MONTHLY PET RENT']
